@startuml variant_b_seq_failover
title Вариант B - failover сценарий (push не получил receipt, SMS доставлено)

participant "Scheduler" as SCH
participant "Orchestrator" as ORC
participant "Saga DB" as SDB
participant "RabbitMQ" as MQ
participant "SMS\nWorker" as SW
participant "SMS\nПровайдер" as SMS
participant "Пользователь" as U

note over SCH : Таймаут receipt истек (5 сек)\nreceipt от FCM не пришел

SCH -> ORC : timeout(saga_id, step = PUSH)
ORC -> SDB : SELECT saga FOR UPDATE\n-- проверяем что ещё не COMPLETED
SDB --> ORC : saga { status = AWAITING_PUSH_RECEIPT }
ORC -> SDB : UPDATE step = SMS, status = FAILOVER

ORC -> MQ : Enqueue sms_task(saga_id)
MQ --> SW : sms_task
SW -> SMS : POST /sms/send
SMS --> SW : 200 OK (sms_id)
SW -> ORC : callback(saga_id, step = SMS, result = SENT)
ORC -> SDB : UPDATE step = AWAITING_SMS_RECEIPT\ntimeout = now + 25s

SMS -> U : SMS
SMS -> ORC : POST /webhook\n{ status: delivered, sms_id }
ORC -> SDB : UPDATE status = COMPLETED

note over U : P99 <= 30 сек от события

@enduml
